'''城塞'''（{{lang-en|Citadel}}）是[[都市|都市]]或[[城鎮|城鎮]]的防禦加固區塊，可能會是一座[[要塞|要塞]]、[[城堡|城堡]]或防禦中心。<ref>{{citebook|title=Castles: Their Construction and History |url=https://archive.org/details/castlestheircons00toys |author= [[Sidney_Toy|Sidney Toy]]|year=1985|publisher=[[Courier_Dover|Courier Dover]]|isbn=0486248984}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/citadel |title=Definition of 'citadel' |accessdate=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216015555/https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/citadel |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Citadel一词来源于[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]「Civis」，意为公民。另有说法“城塞”一词来源于近代早期意大利文「Cittadella」，意为“小城市”。


